public class BooleanVariable
extends BooleanExpr
implements jopt.csp.variable.CspBooleanVariable, Variable

A class used to create a concrete boolean variable with a domain that can be altered. A basic variable with an internal domain can be created or a variable can be created based on a boolean expression or constraint.

Author:
jboerkoel, Nick Coleman
